TEXT.S:
matatengil ku Sakizaya a tedamaw i 2017.7.22 i Sakul niyazu', musakamu ku kamu nu Sakizaya atu Wikipayke a kawaw nu Sakizaya. ahican patizeng ku kamu nu Sakizaya, ahican pacakad ku Wikipayke. uyniyan a maatengil, tayni ci Akamy Coco atu ci Siuzhi namakay Chengzhi tabakiay a cacudadan , musakamu tu Wikipayke atu nuzikuzay a kawaw. ci Akamy Coco atu ci Siuzhi, u tatayna amin, sangulan a kaying, sipunuay a tademaw, matenes tu mikawaw i Chengzhi Tabakiay a cacudadan, maluk kuheni. u ngangan nu matatengil: u kamu atu cudad nu Sakizaya u tuki: 2017.07.22 08:30 icuwa: i Kalingku a kuwan, Sakul niyazu', Sakizaya a zazan 111 mukawaway: patakalisiway a pikaputay i nabakuwan ci Tiway Sayun kakelidan: ci Dungy Sela
tatni micakaay a binawlan: Tuku Sayiun, Lisin Cudad, Yiyang Sayiun, Kulihuisin Sayiun, Bakah Huisin,
